            "style": "",
            "text": "Reuters Institute Digital News Report",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ") and a much more diverse group of small and micro publishers catering to niches. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
